casebody.data:
April 3, 2002

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

01- 2250. In re Beck.

Original Action Involving Parental Rights or Adoption. On motion to dismiss of Judge Joseph J. Vukovich. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C. J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
